## ğŸ“… Notes & Best Practices

- âœ‰ï¸ To get started, export a CSV template from the app.
- âš ï¸ Only use **exact matches** from the lists above. Typos or unknown values will be ignored.
- ğŸ” The `Has Reference Image` column accepts `true` or `false`.
- âœ”ï¸ You can leave non-required fields empty.

